":[{"lineNumber":63,"content":"- 过程话术变体与文档中凡引用「按时段桶筛选」的表述一并去掉。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":224,"content":"| A3 | 列表与场景卡自定义块 | StringList / PromptVariantList / PromptSceneList / LocalHourRange / AvatarUpload |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":232,"content":"| C1 | 读写 `data/characters/<agentId>.json`（经 API 门面） | 保存后磁盘一致；无 `timeBuckets` |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":233,"content":"| C2 | 记忆只读列表 + 分页 | 按 userId 查库；无写口 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false}]},{"file":"docs/AI和人类/里程碑/v2.0/项目第二步计划执行索引.md","matches":[{"lineNumber":31,"content":"  - \"电话壳|Realtime|对标迁移旧话机\"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":125,"content":"| ✅ | V2-P2 | **新建故事包 Modal**：列表页 `FormModal` 触发新建；提交 mock 增或跳编辑器；`/packages/create` 改为薄入口/重定向，主流程不依赖整页 | npm run quality:studio |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":127,"content":"| ✅ | V2-C1 | **新建角色**：「新建角色」可用 `FormModal`；显示名/类型/简介；`agentId` 系统生成；mock 写入可变数据源 | npm run quality:studio |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":128,"content":"| ✅ | V2-C2 | **角色详情全字段编辑**：`CharacterLibraryDetail` 分组展示 identity/persona/social/Free 就绪/引用/agentId 高级区；Formik 编辑态 | npm run quality:studio |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":129,"content":"| ✅ | V2-C3 | **角色删改 mock**：列表删除、详情保存；会话内列表与详情一致 | npm run quality:studio |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":132,"content":"| ✅ | V2-A3 | **资源删改 mock**：同 V2-C3 | npm run quality:studio |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":135,"content":"| ✅ | V2-U3 | **用户删改 mock**：同 V2-C3 | npm run quality:studio |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false}]},{"file":"docs/AI和人类/里程碑/v2.0/项目第一步计划执行索引.md","matches":[{"lineNumber":27,"content":"  - \"接入 Realtime|实现电话壳|对标迁移旧话机\"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":80,"content":"| 新建 `apps/studio