{"type":"tool_call","subtype":"completed","call_id":"call-bb732530-e36a-455c-800c-a13c534bdbf5-60\nfc_709080ac-24e3-93ab-8db6-ba0a5ef9b023_1","tool_call":{"taskToolCall":{"args":{"description":"Scan doubao/xiaoyu usages","prompt":"In /Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine, analyze what needs to change for migrating away from character files doubao-sister and xiaoyu (delete those JSON files after migration).\n\nTask V2-S8-17 requires:\n1. Migrate golden_handoff package and demo-user profile from doubao-sister/xiaoyu to the five characters (prefer lanxing + xiaopi)\n2. Delete data/characters/doubao-sister.json, xiaoyu.json and their free-cards/schedule-cards\n3. Update all engine/studio tests that break\n\nPlease return:\nA) Exact file list under data/ that reference doubao-sister or xiaoyu\nB) Which packages/rpg-engine/tests files READ those character JSON from disk (vs only use as inline string IDs in fixtures)\nC) Recommended ID mapping (doubao-sister→?, xiaoyu→?) considering golden handoff needs dialable:false for unlock target\nD) Whether xiaopi.dialable should become false, or another approach\nE) List of card files in golden_handoff that need ownerAgentId/effect agentId updates\nF) Any free-card files that need creating (xiaopi_free etc.)\n\nBe thorough but concise. Do not modify files.","subagentType":{"unspecified":{}},"model":"default","agentId":"a33ea75c-82ec-45bb-98cf-c0dc15fbbecc","attachments":[],"mode":"TASK_MODE_UNSPECIFIED","respondingToMessageIds":[],"environment":"SUBAGENT_EXECUTION_ENVIRONMENT_UNSPECIFIED"},"result":{"success":{"conversationSteps":[{"assistantMessage":{"text":"我会只做只读分析：先扫 `data/` 与测试里对 `doubao-sister` / `xiaoyu` 的引用，再对照五角色与 golden_handoff 的拨号/解锁需求。## 结论\n\n`doubao-sister` ≈ 旧澜星样例、`xiaoyu` ≈ 需解锁的转介目标。应迁到 **`lanxing`（可拨介绍方）+ `xiaopi`（`dialable:false` 解锁目标）**，再删遗留角色与其 free/schedule 卡。\n\n---\n\n### A) `data/` 中引用 `doubao-sister` / `xiaoyu` 的文件（完整）\n\n| 路径 | 角色 |\n|------|------|\n| `data/characters/doubao-sister.json` | **待删** |\n| `data/characters/xiaoyu.json` | **待删** |\n| `data/characters/free-cards/doubao_free.s-card.json` | **待删** |\n| `data/characters/free-cards/xiaoyu_free.s-card.json` | **待删** |\n| `data/characters/schedule-cards/doubao_morning_checkin.s-card.json` | **迁 owner 后删/改名** |\n| `data/users/demo-user/profile.save.json` | characters / board / redial / lore |\n| `data/storis-packages/golden_handoff/story.conf.json` | participants |\n| `data/storis-packages/golden_handoff/canvas.layout.json` | lanes |\n| `data/storis-packages/golden_handoff/cards/doubao_intro_outbound.s-card.json` | owner + unlock/attach/redial |\n| `data/storis-packages/golden_handoff/cards/xiaoyu_waiting_user.s-card.json` | owner + unmount effects |\n| `data/storis-packages/golden_handoff/cards/doubao_a_writes_b.s-card.json` | owner + knowledge/memory agentId |\n| `data/storis-packages/golden_handoff/cards/demo_playback_hello.s-card.json` | ownerAgentId |\n\n共 **12** 个；无其它 `data/` 命中。\n\n---\n\n### B) 测试：读盘角色 JSON vs 仅字符串 ID\n\n**直接 `readFile` 角色 JSON：**\n\n| 文件 | 读什么 |\n|------|--------|\n| `tests/host/golden-handoff.test.ts` | `characters/xiaoyu.json`（断言 `isEffectiveDialable`） |\n| `tests/validation/golden-handoff.validate.test.ts` | `characters/doubao-sister.json`（改 social → `SOCIAL_TARGET_UNKNOWN`） |\n\n**直接读盘相关 free/schedule（删角色时一并改）：**\n\n| 文件 | 路径 |\n|------|------|\n| `tests/validation/golden-handoff.validate.test.ts` | `free-cards/xiaoyu_free.s-card.json`（删文件测 `FREE_CARD_MISSING`） |\n| `tests/validation/validatePackage.referencedAgents.test.ts` | 同上 |\n| `tests/host/schedule-card-recurring.test.ts` | `schedule-cards/doubao_morning_checkin.s-card.json` |\n\n**仅 fixture 字符串 ID**（不读上述 JSON，但改 ID 后必改断言）：  \n`effect-s11`、`effect-sink-plan-status`、`pick-pending-entry-mode`、`callcard-schema-tighten`、`collectReferencedAgentIds`、`schedule-package-division`、`playback-phase`、`lore/bootstrap-fallback`，以及大量 `host/*-e2e` / `engine-plan-*` / `a-to-b-memory` / `free-call-pipeline` / `manual-story-loop` / `active-story-lock` 等（约 **25+** 文件含 ID）。\n\n**间接依赖磁盘**：凡 `cp(dataSrc)` + `loadWorkspace` / `validatePackage(\"golden_handoff\")` / `beginCall` 的测试都会在删角色后红，即使未显式 `readFile` 角色文件。\n\nStudio（任务范围外但会断）：`apps/studioV2/tests/...` 两处 fixture；旧 `apps/studio` debugger 默认 `doubao-sister`/`xiaoyu`。\n\n---\n\n### C) 推荐 ID 映射\n\n| 旧 | 新 | 理由 |\n|----|----|------|\n| `doubao-sister` | **`lanxing`** | 同人设「澜星」；已有 `dialable:true`、`lanxing_free`、`social.canIntroduce→xiaopi` |\n| `xiaoyu` | **`xiaopi`** | 任务偏好；作 unlock 目标 |\n\n附属（建议同步改测/文案，非强制改文件名）：\n\n- beat：`user_knows_to_call_xiaoyu` → `user_knows_to_call_xiaopi`（多测硬编码）\n- fact：`doubao_shared_xiaoyu_topic` → 如 `lanxing_shared_xiaopi_topic`\n- cardId 可保留 `doubao_*` / `xiaoyu_waiting_user`（只改 agent 字段），或顺手改成 `lanxing_*` / `xiaopi_waiting_user`（测与 conf 改面更大）\n\n`demo-user`：`characters` / `callCards.board` / `telephony.redialSlot` / `world.lore` 键与 agentId 一并换成 `lanxing`/`xiaopi`；起手应 **无 `xiaopi` unlocked**（或 `unlocked:false`），才能复现 golden 不可拨。\n\n---\n\n### D) `xiaopi.dialable` 是否改成 `false`\n\n**应改成 `false`。**\n\n`effectiveDialable = dialable \\|\\| unlocked`。五人目前全是 `dialable:true`，若不改，`set_character_unlocked` **无法**做出「解锁前不可拨」；`golden-handoff.test.ts` 的 `CHARACTER_NOT_DIALABLE` 会失效。\n\n其它做法（不推荐作主方案）：\n\n- 另选解锁目标并设 `dialable:false`（违背 lanxing+xiaopi 偏好）\n- 另造第六人（与删遗留、五人库冲突）\n\n`wrong_number_act1` 引擎测未依赖「小皮默认可拨」；`lanxing.social` 已可 introduce `xiaopi`。产品上「先经澜星转介再拨小皮」也合理。\n\n---\n\n### E) golden_handoff 需改 `ownerAgentId` / effect `agentId` 的卡\n\n| 文件 | 必改字段 |\n|------|----------|\n| `cards/doubao_intro_outbound.s-card.json` | `ownerAgentId`→lanxing；effects：`set_character_unlocked` / `attach_call_card` / `set_redial_slot` 的 `agentId`→xiaopi；`cardId` 若重命名则同步；beats/文案可选 |\n| `cards/xiaoyu_waiting_user.s-card.json` | `ownerAgentId`→xiaopi；`unmount_call_card.agentId`→xiaopi |\n| `cards/doubao_a_writes_b.s-card.json` | `ownerAgentId`→lanxing；`update_npc_knowledge` / `patch_memory` 的 `agentId`→xiaopi |\n| `cards/demo_playback_hello.s-card.json` | 仅 `ownerAgentId`→lanxing |\n\n另：**非 cards 但同包**：`story.conf.json`（participants）、`canvas.layout.json`（lanes）。\n\n---\n\n### F) 需新建的 free-card\n\n| 文件 | 必要？ |\n|------|--------|\n| **`data/characters/free-cards/xiaopi_free.s-card.json`** | **必须**。`xiaopi.json` 已声明 `freeCardId: \"xiaopi_free\"`，磁盘缺失；一旦包引用 `xiaopi`，`validatePackage` → `FREE_CARD_MISSING`。可仿 `lanxing_free`（`cardKind:\"free\"`，`ownerAgentId:\"xiaopi\"`）。 |\n| `lanxing_free` | 已存在，无需新建 |\n| `qiang_shushu_free` / `zhang_boss_free` / `bai_bansian_free` | 本任务不必；仅当某包引用到对应 agent 时 validate 才查 free 卡 |\n\nSchedule：不要只删 `doubao_morning_checkin`；应 **改 `ownerAgentId→lanxing`**（建议改名为 `lanxing_morning_checkin` 并改测里的 `scheduleCardId`），否则 schedule 回归会断。\n\n删除清单（迁移完成后）：`doubao-sister.json`、`xiaoyu.json`、`doubao_free`、`xiaoyu_free`、旧 `doubao_morning_checkin`（若已改名）。"}}],"agentId":"65323379-baa2-411c-96f1-f66cbf490790","isBackground":false,"durationMs":"74948","backgroundReason":"SUBAGENT_BACKGROUND_REASON_UNSPECIFIED"}}},"hookAdditionalContexts":[],"toolCallId":"call-bb732530-e36a-455c-800c-a13c534bdbf5-60\nfc_709080ac-24e3-93ab-8db6-ba0a5ef9b023_1","startedAtMs":"1784770717308","completedAtMs":"1784770792258"},"model_call_id":"a4ddf5ab-bdf9-4190-9892-f4da1b574d4b-12-cvhx","session_id":"086c6681-fcf7-46d9-8405-ea9407b78f48","timestamp_ms":1784770792200}
